92 is all the more dear and pleasing to God
93 as she is more solitary in doing good;

106 But if the shameless women were certain
107 of what the swift heavens are preparing for them,
108 they would already have their mouths open to scream;

127 He speaks so much of making me his companion
128 that I will be where Beatrice is;
129 here it is necessary that I remain without him.
